      "border_only": true,
      "type": "story",
      "text": "Cookie loads bullets into his revolver with a faraway gaze. You get the sense this isn't the first time he's woken to such trauma. \"We're gonna find 'em,\" he intones over and over under his breath. \"We're gonna find 'em.\" You're unsure who he is trying to convince."
